Kia ora Raffaella,
Thank you for your email and for raising your concerns.
We want to assure you that we are investigating the privacy matter you've h=
ighlighted and will get back to you as soon as possible with an update.
Your request for the outstanding documents has been forwarded to the releva=
nt team. We are also looking into why these were missed, and have escalated=
 the urgency. You can expect a response with the outstanding content by clo=
se of business on 24 October 2025.
Thank you again, and please accept our sincere apologies for the inconvenie=
nce caused.
Regards
[cid:image001.png@01DC3C1F.284D7590]
Privacy Team
Level 5, 136 Fanshawe Street,
PO Box 90347, Auckland 1142
[Text  Description automatically generated with low confidence]
